20... Bg7 21. Rg1 Kh8 22. Be3
{ White naturally brings the last piece into the game before advancing any pawns on the kingside. Black has no counterplay so White has all the time in the world to slowly improve the position of all the pieces. }
22... Ng8 23. g5
