26. a5 { Good alternatives included b2-b3 as well as chopping on b5. } 26...
Na4 27. Qd2 h4 28. Nf5 { Moving up the board is the only way forward! } 28...
d5 29. Ne5 { is the final accurate move, giving White a very big advantage. } *

