9. Ne2 { Neutralizes Black's active knight. } 9... Nxe2
{ 9...Ne6  10.Bc4  O-O  11.h6±  is problematic for Black. } 10. Bxe2
{ White is now ready to force concessions with h6. Black should naturally stop this by playing }
10... h6 { himself. } 11. d3 a5
