13... h6
{ happened in the game1-0 @@StartBracket@@54@@EndBracket@@ Svane, F @@StartBracket@@2421@@EndBracket@@-Acs, G @@StartBracket@@1977@@EndBracket@@ Chess.com INT 2020. Here White played the unnecessary  14.Be3?!  This move makes little sense. As mentioned before, Black is going to expand with ...f5-f4 which will hit White's e3 bishop. There's absolutely no reason to be subject to such a tempo. }
14. Qb3
{ This is an improvement over the aforementioned game. By retreating the queen, White liberates the path of the a2-pawn. }
14... f5
{ We can cope with this threat by setting up the typical f2-f3 blockade: } 15.
Nd2 g5 16. a4 Nf6 17. f3
