{ 18.Bb6  is possible, but leads to a mess after some queen sacrifices. } 18...
Rxc7 19. Nb6 { Leads to a forced sequence of moves... } 19... Rd8 20. Bg5
{ The double-attack on the rook and queen forces the knight to go back. } 20...
Ne7 21. Qe4 Nf6 22. Bxf6 Bxf6 23. Nd5
