13. O-O-O
{ 13.g5?!  is premature on account of  13...f5  14.O-O-O  fxe4  15.Qxe4  Qe7  followed by ...Bf5 with good play. }
13... Be6 14. g5 f5 { is a blunder. } 15. g6 h6 16. Bxh6
