11. a4
{ White grabs space on the queenside and will continue with b2-b4 next if allowed. }
11... a5
{ What else? Black can't give White free hand on the queenside. But now comes a typical and beautiful shot! }
12. c5
{ A thematic break, not giving Black any time to even think about starting kingside operations. }
