9. Nbd2 Bf8 10. d4 b5 11. Bc2 Bb7 12. a3
{ is a nice prelude to the knight tour, ruling out ...exd4 followed by ...Nb4.   12.d5  is another possibility, opting for the d5-c4-b3 pawn chain. 1-0 @@StartBracket@@43@@EndBracket@@ Popovic,P @@StartBracket@@2510@@EndBracket@@ -Vujosevic,V @@StartBracket@@2380@@EndBracket@@ Banja Vrucica 1991 is an instructive game on how to handle White's position. }
12... g6 13. Nf1 Bg7 14. Ng3
