8. Bg5
{ Prevents ...Nxe4 by pinning the knight. White is now threatening dxe5.   8.dxe5  is another possibility. The mainline goes  8...Nxe4  9.Qd5  Nc5  10.Bc2  Ne7  11.Qd1  d5!  Black is fine in all the ensuing lines. }
