{ And there's no need to worry about Black's play on the queenside. For example }
19... c4 { is bypassed by } 20. b4 { and } 20... a5
{ is strongly met by the counterblow } 21. a4
{ Boom! It's now clear that Black's play on the queenside only weakened his position. }
