13... Bc5
{ 13...Rc8  loses material to  14.Nb3  Rxc2  15.Nxd4±  forking the c2 rook and the e6 bishop. }
14. Nb3 Bb6 15. Bf4 { A simple yet effective way to pick up the d4-pawn. }
15... Rc8 16. Rac1
{ Simply protecting the c2-pawn. White is undoubtedly better as the d4 pawn is about to drop. }
