[FEN "r1b2rk1/2q1bppp/pn1p1n2/1p1Pp3/P1P1P3/2P2N1P/2B2PP1/RNBQR1K1 b - - 0 15"]
[SetUp "1"]

15... bxa4 { Black has just played ...bxa4. Was this a good idea? } 16. c5
{ Not at all easy to spot, but this pawn sacrifice nets White a big advantage.   16.Bxa4  yields very little. After  16...Bd7  17.Bxd7  Nbxd7  White's extra c-pawn is useless and likely to fall shortly. }
16... Qxc5 { 16...dxc5  17.Bxa4 } 17. Nxe5 dxe5 18. Ba3 Qc7 19. d6
{ recoups the sacrificed piece with interest. } *

